@host = http://localhost:5038

### 1. Create IQ Test with Visual Option
POST {{host}}/api/IqTests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test de Inteligencia Visual",
  "description": "Evaluación de razonamiento visual",
  "totalTimeMinutes": 30,
  "isActive": true,
  "sections": [
    {
      "name": "Razonamiento Lógico",
      "orderIndex": 1,
      "questions": [
        {
          "text": "¿Qué figura completa la secuencia?",
          "imageUrl": "https://example.com/question1.png",
          "questionType": "multiple_choice",
          "score": 10,
          "abilityDomain": "Logic",
          "options": [
            { "text": "Opción A", "optionKey": "A", "imageUrl": "https://example.com/optA.png", "isCorrect": false },
            { "text": "Opción B", "optionKey": "B", "imageUrl": "https://example.com/optB.png", "isCorrect": true },
            { "text": "Opción C", "optionKey": "C", "imageUrl": "https://example.com/optC.png", "isCorrect": false }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

### 2. Assign Test to Group 1 (Active)
POST {{host}}/api/IqTests/assign
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "testId": 1,
  "groupId": 1,
  "isActive": true,
  "startDate": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2025-12-31T23:59:59Z"
}

### 3. Get Active Test for Student 1 (Assuming Student 1 is in Group 1)
GET {{host}}/api/IqTests/student/1/active
Accept: application/json

### 4. Submit IQ Test for Student 1
POST {{host}}/api/IqTests/submit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": 1,
  "testId": 1,
  "startedAt": "2024-02-12T10:00:00Z",
  "answers": [
    {
      "questionId": 1,
      "selectedOptionId": 2 
    }
  ]
}

### 5. Verify Student Profile Updated (Expect IqScore = ~160 due to 100% score)
GET {{host}}/api/StudentProfile/1
Accept: application/json
